        "## Leveraging Remote Repositories for Collaboration\n",
        "Remote repositories facilitate team collaboration by hosting a central version of the codebase. Platforms like GitHub, GitLab, and Bitbucket enable distributed teams to share updates, review changes, and synchronize their work efficiently. The remote repository acts as the definitive source of truth for the project.\n",
